{"tid":1514452,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"十年呢套電影 未到2025年 已經兌現哂！香港必須獨立！","createTime":"2019-08-28T17:48:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-28T20:07:04.000Z","uid":66390,"like":50,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"aaf4eee615887c1b6448afae3b8de9685920a999","tid":1514452,"uid":66390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T17:48:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jomVE9r.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjomVE9r.png&h=6dc8b01e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V99j6Px.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV99j6Px.png&h=24f7202f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OknBpBc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOknBpBc.png&h=c13a8c45&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QoP0RgA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQoP0RgA.jpg&h=b2fcf823&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/03mVE9W.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F03mVE9W.jpg&h=c7cf4bbe&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0YBq2oi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0YBq2oi.jpg&h=b3fbce49&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NHy5hWF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNHy5hWF.jpg&h=e33dab05&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vZBB83m.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvZBB83m.jpg&h=01cc1f8c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tHMKyu5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtHMKyu5.jpg&h=67139724&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zcTQt3q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzcTQt3q.jpg&h=d07640fa&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9dcmAJr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9dcmAJr.jpg&h=8e49a9c9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Jykn4BN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJykn4BN.jpg&h=0d5843fa&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F1sJO3t.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF1sJO3t.jpg&h=010e110a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">各位 基本法唔係不可侵犯 基本法可以修改 可以廢除<br />\n當被問到身份認同時 大家都會答「香港人」<br />\n呢種民族意識既建構 已經有條件成立一個國家<br />\n只係大家唔敢踏出呢一步<br />\n<br />\n中英聯合聲明講到 除左國防 外交外 其他事一律由港人負責 中央不能干預<br />\n<br />\n事至今天 我地仲要同佢地講法律 講條文 講基本法咩？<br />\n請放下潔癖 將「香港獨立」呢個思想植入腦海<br />\n先視為夢想 目標 慢慢實踐<br />\n<br />\n香港人要學識突破 要真正接納「無野係無可能嫁」<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CnX9KDT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCnX9KDT.png&h=bcf6b209&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3LEzVLy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3LEzVLy.png&h=535db3c9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cFjPKDT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcFjPKDT.png&h=4b64526f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港人<br />\n我地仲有時間<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港獨立</span></span>"},{"pid":"9ed14e89961af5f6d94a583f4bcbe283fef76108","tid":1514452,"uid":66390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T17:49:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"268ba0cfe9dad92a7cf7a6a771b74531636d5d6c","tid":1514452,"uid":66390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T17:49:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.g